<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Tzotzil_language&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1" title="Edit section: Phonology">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline" id="Phonology">Phonology</span></h2>
<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Tzotzil_language&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2" title="Edit section: Vowels">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline" id="Vowels">Vowels</span></h3>
<p>Tzotzil has five vowels. o and u can fluctuate between <a href="/wiki/Roundedness" title="Roundedness">rounded</a> and <a href="/wiki/Unrounded" title="Unrounded" class="mw-redirect">unrounded</a>.</p>
